snippet.title: Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Complete Edition - Battle Gameplay Trailer | NSW, PC
snippet.description:
The most brilliant hackers always come prepared for battle in Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Complete Edition. Check out this new trailer for some tips on how to get the best of your digital-opponents when this exciting turn based title releases on October 18th, 2019 for #NintendoSwitch and #PC! Which #Digimon will you choose to build your ultimate team? Pre-order your copy today: https://bandainam.co/DigimonCSCE
